title: LinPlug Element P v1.1.0b Incl. Keygen-R2R [deepstatus]
description:
LinPlug Element P v1.1.0b





The Element P is a specialized synthesizer for percussion sounds. It creates sounds using a simplified FM synthesis method, which is simple and easy to operate.



Specification


Code
specialized percussion synthesizer
unique sound
24-voice polyphonic
decent and easy to understand set of parameters
unique virtual analogue sound engine.
special oscillator, similar to FM synthesis
four envelopes for pitch, timbre, noise and volume
all parameters addressable via MIDI controllers
200+ presets included to get you started.


   PC computer with at least 500 MHz CPU
   VST capable host software (DAW), like Cubase, Logic, Orion, FL Studio etc
   ElementP itself requires about 16 Mb memory only (first instance, 6 Mb for all additional instances)
   a Screen resolution of 1024 x 768 or better
   Windows XP and newer, any Processor
   Element P comes as both native 32 bit and 64 bit plugin





Installation

1.Uninstall previous versions.
2.Install the plugin.
3.Use our keygen on Windows, or serials provided to register.
